Incoming livestream: It documents the 12 categories of threats for MCP.

229
00:23:48.793 --> 00:23:52.172
Incoming livestream: And it also talks about the various controls.

230
00:23:52.313 --> 00:23:54.112
Incoming livestream: To mitigate the threats.

231
00:23:54.843 --> 00:24:02.623
Incoming livestream: Confidential computing is called out as a important security control for multiple security threats. So.

232
00:24:02.633 --> 00:24:17.303
Incoming livestream: If you have interest in this, I would say look for COSI, look for their MCP paper. It is public, it's available, there is no cost for it. I would strongly, urge you to take a look at that paper, because it's a very well-written paper.

